-- Saudi Electricity Awards 1.2 Billion Riyals in Contracts for Power Project
-- Inal Ersan
-- 2010-09-20T08:59:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/saudi-electricity-awards-1-2-billion-riyals-in-contracts-for-power-project.html

          
          
             Saudi Electricity Co. awarded three
contracts valued at a total of 1.2 billion riyals to link
exisiting power stations, build a new one and expand another,
the official Saudi Press Agency reported.  
 The agency, citing Chief Executive Officer Ali al-Barrak,
did not name the companies that won the contracts.  
